@startuml elogistics-address-workflow

title Address Selection, Customization & Verification Workflow

|Dispatcher|
start
:Start typing in name field;

|Frontend|
:Display options;
:Send search request to Backend;

|Backend|
:Request address search via API;

|eLogistics Portal|
:Search for matching contacts;
:Return matching contacts with addresses;

|Backend|
:Forward contact options;

|Frontend|
:Display contact & address options;

|Dispatcher|
if (Contact & Address contained?) then (no)
  :Enter custom name and address;
else (yes)
  :Select matching proposal\n(contact incl. address);
endif

:Click "Save";

|Frontend|
:Send persist request to Backend;

|Backend|
:Request to save Transport Order\nvia TMS Bridge;

|TMS Bridge|
:Call pDis_TransportOrder.Save()\n(TransportOrder details + address info);

|TMS Database|
:Store Transport Order with\ncontact & address snapshot;
:Return success;

|TMS Bridge|
:Return success;

|Backend|
:Return success;

|Frontend|
:Display success notification;

|Dispatcher|
stop

@enduml
